OL,3,C14 injured at funfair after children's
OL,4,Cride appears to derail
OL,6,F14 people have been injured after a
OL,7,Fchildren's roller coaster appeared to
OL,8,Fderail at a funfair in Porthcawl,
OL,9,Fsouth Wales.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FConey Beach Amusement Park just before
OL,13,F6pm on Wednesday evening after an
OL,14,Fincident involving one of the rides.
OL,16,F13 children and one adult have
OL,17,Fsustained 'minor injuries', with seven
OL,18,Fpeople requiring hospital treatment,
OL,19,Femergency services have confirmed.
