OL,6,FConey Beach Amusement Park said the
OL,7,Fincident involved a "third-party ride
OL,8,Fnot owned by Coney Beach".
OL,10,FOne eyewitness told ITV News she heard
OL,11,Fscreams as ambulances rushed to the
OL,12,Fscene.
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police said that the area
OL,15,Fwill remain closed tomorrow while
OL,16,Finvestigations are carried out.
OL,18,FPeople have been urged to avoid the
OL,19,Farea.
