OL,6,FOn Wednesday evening, South Wales
OL,7,FPolice said: "Officers were called to
OL,8,FConey Beach Amusement Park, Porthcawl,
OL,9,FBridgend at around 5:50pm this evening
OL,10,F(Wednesday August 13) following an
OL,11,Faccident involving one of the rides.
OL,13,F"At this time we have confirmed that
OL,14,F13 children and one adult have
OL,15,Fsustained minor injuries. Some of
OL,16,Fthese have required hospital treatment.
OL,18,F"The amusement park will remain closed
OL,19,Ftomorrow while officers and health and
OL,20,Fsafety personnel carry out their
OL,21,Finvestigation.
