OL,6,F"Please continue to avoid the area to
OL,7,Fallow Emergency Services access."
OL,9,FA Welsh Ambulance Service spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "We were called shortly before
OL,11,F18:00 to reports of an incident at
OL,12,FConey Beach, Porthcawl.
OL,14,F"We sent three emergency ambulances,
OL,15,Fthree Cymru high acuity response unit
OL,16,Fparamedics, two duty operational
OL,17,Fmanagers and our Hazardous Area
OL,18,FResponse Team to the scene.
OL,20,F"Seven patients were taken to hospital
OL,21,Fby ambulance for further treatment."
