OL,4,Cride appears to derail
OL,6,FIn a statement on social media, Coney
OL,7,FBeach Amusement Park said: "Due to an
OL,8,Fincident on a third-party ride not
OL,9,Fowned by Coney Beach, we were
OL,10,Finstructed by the police to clear the
OL,11,Fsite for further investigation.
OL,13,F"We apologise for the disruption and
OL,14,Fwill be providing refunds to affected
OL,15,Fguests as soon as possible. We will be
OL,16,Freleasing instructions on refunds
OL,17,Fshortly."
