OL,6,FThe amusement park announced earlier
OL,7,Fthis year that it would be closing its
OL,8,Fgates for good in October after more
OL,9,Fthan 100 years in operation.
OL,11,FWhat's the history of Coney Beach in
OL,12,FPorthcawl?
OL,14,FConey Beach Amusement Park dates back
OL,15,Fto 1918.
OL,17,FIt is thought to have been built to
OL,18,Fentertain American troops returning
OL,19,Ffrom the First World War, taking its
OL,20,Fname from the New York pleasure park
OL,21,Fon Coney Island.
