OL,6,FConey Beach experienced a significant
OL,7,Fboom in popularity in the 1950s,
OL,8,Fdrawing large crowds with events like
OL,9,Fboxing matches, firework displays, and
OL,10,Faerial acrobat shows.
OL,12,FThe planned closure paves the way for
OL,13,Fthe Porthcawl Waterfront Regeneration
OL,14,FProject, a joint initiative by
OL,15,FBridgend Council and the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment.
